{"tid":1152086,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"轉行的抉擇","createTime":"2019-05-12T17:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T11:02:38.000Z","uid":68254,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c952ab75368999523abebd626be3b591634ec0","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"之前睇過有巴打開post<br />\n話係香港做設計係搵唔到食，冇出路<br />\n<br />\n其實個派直到依家，我都係咁想轉行⋯<br />\n我係做時裝設計，但好景不常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊年間公司因為蝕錢為由向幾位同事開刀，<br />\n而我就係其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我前後就做過幾間不同的時裝公司<br />\n其中有間A公司，請左我返去，日日俾說話我聽<br />\n當我狗咁喝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都算，每日都增加我工作範圍<br />\n其實當時我咪當學野，點知佢見我好恰<br />\n<br />\n就成日串我，話有啲布公司唔要，話我想要可以拎返去用<br />\n我原本好開心想拎返去車圍裙，點知佢係要串我一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老闆娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：喔～聽講你好似係住公屋架呵？<br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係啊，做咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 你同你奶奶住架喎～你拎咁多野返屋企會唔會俾奶奶罵呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：冇問題喔～～我個房有個地台可以收埋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 乜依家啲公屋有咁大架咩？收唔收得曬呀你？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 得⋯⋯我有方法的了。<br />\n<br />\n之後佢更串我：做設計就係咁架啦！玩唔起呢個遊戲就唔好玩～～<br />\n<br />\n最後頂佢唔順，走左。<br />\n離職當天，佢仲問我可唔可以幫佢帶啲布板去佢舖路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然冇應承<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n之後去左間做批發的時裝公司，今次下定決心要努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都要努力做好份工，但原來設計呢行真係人夾人⋯⋯。無論點努力，最後都係取決於上司對你嘅印象同感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢同時請左我同另一個人返工，事後感覺佢係二選一<br />\n但佢當時係叫我帶住另一個人，因為佢係fresh grad<br />\n咁我就乜都教俾個位同事，有咩都同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後個老闆係復活節假期前夕，夜晚十一點半左右打來<br />\n話我唔係好適合佢地公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯<br />\n<br />\n而當晚我仲同舊同事傾緊用咩方法可以再做好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n我已經對呢行失去信心，亦對自己失去信心<br />\n<br />\n但之前公司的同事都叫我唔好放棄，話我係佢地咁多個之中較色配色係最準，好睇⋯⋯<br />\n但配色好還好，始終款式上係技不如人係我不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊又返份新工，但同時又咁岩有份文職搵我見工<br />\n依家好似人生交叉點咁，如果行左一條錯路⋯就一世<br />\n<br />\n究竟我應該堅持繼續做設計，定轉行算了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcfd0ad09ab304592f0518dbeadcb9e6e2f78c1","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:35:52.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，打太長⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9876d90b3ae791ad7632d20c32ec6e17ad47f2","tid":1152086,"uid":16775,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:45:54.000Z","msg":"完全唔識呢行既野<br />\n但見到你咁努力想同你講聲加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56e31f1d68671cc63a28db87cb63046282b2090","tid":1152086,"uid":245106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:47:56.000Z","msg":"睇到都覺得慘<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236b2b6148e881db1e6a13eb1834f92dad4a33e9","tid":1152086,"uid":103647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:47:59.000Z","msg":"設計其他野唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8efa7976eda7561e7d7384a75a63a468d93102","tid":1152086,"uid":70417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:50:31.000Z","msg":"文職幾時都轉到，唔洗諗啦下話"},{"pid":"65226b3174f7ec7bd0ed5155a4180390b4189a34","tid":1152086,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:53:22.000Z","msg":"呢行人工如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9728c93b85bdadb0242e4ddae81f81ca1100f391","tid":1152086,"uid":245742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65226b3174f7ec7bd0ed5155a4180390b4189a34","tid":1152086,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:53:22.000Z","msg":"呢行人工如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"我都想知，再升一級要用幾長又幾多？$"},{"pid":"00131909e11b53ab76549a3595c0f4151646eede","tid":1152086,"uid":189611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f822adcea878707ba402cd894506bbaf7781e6","tid":1152086,"uid":209140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:00:11.000Z","msg":"堅持，雖然好難，但你真係只差啲際遇，終有日會有回報㗎喇，加油"},{"pid":"b8957db249b217f4212b1377d31edce19508f3d4","tid":1152086,"uid":192327,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:05:41.000Z","msg":"老實仲有團火就堅持 你都係差少少人際同伯樂"},{"pid":"98926d0022e3ffe46c155eeb255bf541fe28ed4a","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"236b2b6148e881db1e6a13eb1834f92dad4a33e9","tid":1152086,"uid":103647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:47:59.000Z","msg":"設計其他野唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:11:19.000Z","msg":"之前做過兩年設計鞋，但想轉返去時裝設計⋯<br />\n因為當初係入唔到時裝設計呢行，先入做鞋設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790f4cf061fe577acebf1c827d2ddcf550e3495c","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"65226b3174f7ec7bd0ed5155a4180390b4189a34","tid":1152086,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:53:22.000Z","msg":"呢行人工如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:13:44.000Z","msg":"以前我有個朋友Fresh grad入行價9K<br />\n我對上份工果個fresh grad入行價12.5K<br />\n<br />\n不過都係個句，睇際遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ee14a2cfa2e0b6c841bac110633a4f52fe9716","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00131909e11b53ab76549a3595c0f4151646eede","tid":1152086,"uid":189611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:16:45.000Z","msg":"我都想入大公司，但唔係咁易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n競爭好很大⋯個個一讀完書就係想向大公司狗衝<br />\n位又得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯最後其他落選只可做細公司<br />\n甚至行都入唔到，我同屆畢業的同學好多都轉左行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06dbdca58b5750e1d3642390b6b46d8214d5d65","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9728c93b85bdadb0242e4ddae81f81ca1100f391","tid":1152086,"uid":245742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65226b3174f7ec7bd0ed5155a4180390b4189a34","tid":1152086,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:53:22.000Z","msg":"呢行人工如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"我都想知，再升一級要用幾長又幾多？$"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:19:42.000Z","msg":"真係好唔定，我試過衰到加得500蚊。<br />\n但都試過有公司比較好加2000，但工作量跟份糧一齊加"},{"pid":"a6197f3477ad1a8ea3406dfde95d0451f34ec9b0","tid":1152086,"uid":132262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"唔係等住開飯就堅持！<br />\n我相信你係得既！"},{"pid":"641a833a2ea8467fb6769165571d2cba2d8d37ea","tid":1152086,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:21:26.000Z","msg":"似係做20年都上唔到30k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e134a30a9847789eb6a5df92787a03fb255633","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5f822adcea878707ba402cd894506bbaf7781e6","tid":1152086,"uid":209140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:00:11.000Z","msg":"堅持，雖然好難，但你真係只差啲際遇，終有日會有回報㗎喇，加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:22:07.000Z","msg":"多謝您<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯原本我以為會好多人叫我放棄轉行算<br />\n無論最後決定係點，都會記得有人支持自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8b8d4c407b40646d2329bddb3bbfc5f5e1385c","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"641a833a2ea8467fb6769165571d2cba2d8d37ea","tid":1152086,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:21:26.000Z","msg":"似係做20年都上唔到30k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:24:09.000Z","msg":"我係jobsdb見到design director 先有25-30K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知要幾耐先爬到上去⋯⋯⋯仲要唔係得我一個人爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68668c4b0deed42fa79acab9ee5d6246703dc663","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6197f3477ad1a8ea3406dfde95d0451f34ec9b0","tid":1152086,"uid":132262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"唔係等住開飯就堅持！<br />\n我相信你係得既！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"雖然係唔等開飯，但有時好怕不得不向現實低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當份文職仲高人工過做設計時，就會出現抉擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078268f424d512608640d215ad842bd05de04231","tid":1152086,"uid":18564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"轉另一份工你會唔會鐘意先？<br />\n我從字裡行間都感覺到你對時裝設計有熱誠<br />\n但你想係公司跟人要求做野（做打工仔一定係咁）<br />\n定係其實只想係公司學野打好個底再出去發展？<br />\n轉文職係咪完全放棄時裝設計？<br />\n定想正職打工副業設計？<br />\n定或者做freelance可以夠你支出？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都有轉行煩惱 但都係唔知點好"},{"pid":"96240f6108ce03a8a5fb7f007cab2019f4840c92","tid":1152086,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68668c4b0deed42fa79acab9ee5d6246703dc663","tid":1152086,"uid":68254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6197f3477ad1a8ea3406dfde95d0451f34ec9b0","tid":1152086,"uid":132262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"唔係等住開飯就堅持！<br />\n我相信你係得既！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"雖然係唔等開飯，但有時好怕不得不向現實低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當份文職仲高人工過做設計時，就會出現抉擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:30:49.000Z","msg":"每個成功既人都經歷過呢啲少回報或者冇回報既時期<br />\n只要你捱過左。。。就會見到光明<br />\n你將來一定好成功<br />\n你要相信自己"},{"pid":"a668297ccc8952684178ea7cffb79a206f68187f","tid":1152086,"uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"現實同理想，無話選擇邊個錯<br />\n揀左唔好後悔，努力做好，令自己開心就得<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8eb00549087123c9df4b06bdbb9922321dbb2a8","tid":1152086,"uid":248552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T00:36:28.000Z","msg":"真係鐘意做設計嘅話 不如試下轉室內設計<br />\n識人做緊室內設計 人工都唔差 講緊5/6年已經接近30k<br />\n反正你有設計底 轉做室內設計應該唔難 但我諗要由低做起"},{"pid":"efc1705815eb1a956b231801d0fcae8d35fa00a4","tid":1152086,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T00:47:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}